00:04:50.220 --> 00:04:51.820
Make sure when you come up,

00:04:51.820 --> 00:04:52.960
pants that come down,

00:04:52.960 --> 00:04:55.189
you got something under
that ain't going to

00:04:55.189 --> 00:04:56.336
